    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Works used as test-pieces, often by apprentices, and presented to a guild to determine whether the makers were qualified to rank as masters.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
